This Fantastic Rhinestone Ring is adjustable and is an absolute must for any occassion, these Rhinestone rings really are very Blingy.Comes Gift Boxed. 

Originally Rhinestones were rock crystal gathered from the river Rhine. The avaliability was greatly increased in the 18th century when the Alsation Jeweller Georg Friedrich Strass had the idea to imitate diamonds by coating the lower side of the glass with metal powder, hence Rhinestones are called Strass in many european languages. Rhinestones are used as imitation diamonds.

name: Stunning Jade Necklace and Earrings
description:
This stunning Necklace and Earring set will be Gift Wrapped 
Jade has long been a sacred stone in the orient and it was included with chinese grave goods to give vitality to the deceased. It was used for weather magic being forcefully thrown into water to call up snow, mist or rain. A protector against danger for children, Jade can undo physical harm. This stone is a symbol of purity. serenity and nuturing and is a dream stone. Jade stabilises the personality and intergrates mind and body. This stone encourages becoming who you really are, recognising yorself as a spiritual being on a human journey.
